name: DEADLYSINS
description:
Some people afraid to sin, and some other easily do it. Lust, Gluttony, Greed, Sloth, Wrath, Envy, and Pride are some of the main bad attitude in human which always be the start for Crime, Destruction, and Cruelty. They are part of this life, realized or not, those sin stay inside ourself, growing and developing. They wont leave, they wont stop, escorting us to Death.
Artwork: Vidi Nurhadi Ranadipura
